Changes Made:
1. tweets.slice.ts - Redux State Management
Added displayedCount and itemsPerPage to the state (initialized to 5 each)
Added two new reducers:
loadMoreTweets: Increases displayedCount by 5 when scrolling to bottom
resetPagination: Resets displayedCount back to 5 on refresh
Updated all extraReducers to reset pagination on fetch
2. TweetList.tsx - UI Implementation
Show only first 5 tweets initially using slice(0, displayedCount)
Pull-to-Refresh: Dispatches fetchUserTweets and resetPagination to reload fresh data with first 5 items
Infinite Scroll: onEndReached handler triggers loadMoreTweets when user scrolls to bottom
onEndReachedThreshold set to 0.5 for smooth loading
